Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:27.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.06,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:33.08,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:39.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:49.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:59.22,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:02.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:05.62,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.90,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.42,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.36,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.46,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.13,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.61,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:49.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.80,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:27.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有盡頭的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:31.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不見的羽翼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:33.08,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遙遠的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:39.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不見的未來依舊在等待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.42,0:01:49.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不願清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:52.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:59.22,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包圍 誰也逃不出這個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:02.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:05.62,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變幻不定的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.90,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.42,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:21.36,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方聽聞的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:25.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震動鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:36.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我漸漸清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:39.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:42.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.61,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏不斷變化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:49.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的傷口 是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:53.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因為你和Burst The Gravity
